                <a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="#comment-491499" data-commentid="491499" data-postid="1910" data-belowelement="comment-491499" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Carla" aria-label="Reply to Carla">Reply</a>                            </div><!-- .comment-meta -->
			
			<p>Yes I&#8217;m still here! Glad you enjoyed the recipe and great idea using the bulb in salads.</p>

	        </div><!-- #comment-## -->
	 
	    </li><!-- #comment-## -->
</ul><!-- .children -->
</li><!-- #comment-## -->
