                <time pubdate datetime="2021-11-07T19:26:07-05:00">
                November 7, 2021 @ 7:26 PM                </time>
                
                <a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="#comment-503335" data-commentid="503335" data-postid="1910" data-belowelement="comment-503335" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Carla" aria-label="Reply to Carla">Reply</a>                            </div><!-- .comment-meta -->
			
			<p>Oh fun! Might need a second suitcase when you’re done 😂</p>

