	    <li class="comment odd alt thread-even depth-1" id="li-comment-494014">
	        <div id="comment-494014" class="comment">
            
            		
            <div class="post-meta comment-meta">
            	<strong>Anne</strong>            	 &#8212; 
                <time pubdate datetime="2021-08-28T16:14:51-04:00">
                August 28, 2021 @ 4:14 PM                </time>
                
                <a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="#comment-494014" data-commentid="494014" data-postid="1910" data-belowelement="comment-494014" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Anne" aria-label="Reply to Anne">Reply</a>                            </div><!-- .comment-meta -->
			
			<p>I just made this soup,  mostly followed directions,   and I asked my husband to taste it.  Well. 8 &#8211; 10 spoonfuls later her grinned  and said it was great.  Thank you for this recipe!</p>

	        </div><!-- #comment-## -->
	 
	    <ul class="children">
	    <li class="comment byuser comment-author-chocolatemooseyblogadmin bypostauthor even depth-2" id="li-comment-494039">
	        <div id="comment-494039" class="comment">
            
            		
